{"tid":425780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登仔又炒車]碧基澄清無意退出西班牙國家隊","createTime":"2017-10-06T04:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T05:04:58.000Z","uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"771125fa8f9563f40902e784362f9ff74b83c0ba","tid":425780,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"西班牙只要於10月7日擊敗阿爾巴尼亞，就有機會於世界盃外圍賽G組出線。記者會上，比賽卻完全被碧基有關加泰羅尼亞公投一事蓋過，這個巴塞隆拿中堅明言無意退出國家隊，而且反駁與拉莫斯不和一事，指二人關係甚佳。<br />\n<br />\n無人可質疑我對西班牙國家隊的投入」<br />\n<br />\n親皇馬傳媒《馬卡報》的3.4萬人投票中，有63%人認為獨立主義者不應為西班牙國家隊效力，加上操練時球迷喝倒彩，參與加泰羅尼亞公投的碧基已成為西班牙國家隊中不受歡迎人物。這個巴塞後衛對被噓感難過，不過無意退隊︰「無人可質疑我對西班牙國家隊的投入，會繼續協助球隊，聽從教練的話。大家不會意見一致，我支持加泰公投，同樣尊重與我政見不同的人。重要的是互相尊重及溝通。」近日有傳與中堅拍檔沙治奧拉莫斯的關係破裂，碧基強烈否認︰「那傳聞是假的，我們關係很好，沒有問題。我們會繼續成為拍檔（partners in a business）。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被問到對加泰獨立的立場，碧基未有正面回應︰「這是100萬元的問題，我不能回答。</span>足球員是公眾人物，我不能站在一邊。現在政治形勢很困難，只有溝通才能解決。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5047caa7688bf7068ceb629b1f99e8420a8c7a79","tid":425780,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/123936_4f3e04fa5c13a845018cc61bf7489971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F123936_4f3e04fa5c13a845018cc61bf7489971.jpg&h=c33b3448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n退出左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b155442cf13cd20f059717a8521152c1ae36b3","tid":425780,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81ba39d457a05c4b4e2c764dcc48550b2c1aef8e","tid":425780,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"炒車是連登新常態"},{"pid":"ec35af779f4df387a788ee99f47d44d1c300cb0e","tid":425780,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"巴塞球星碧基︰若親加泰立場構成問題，願意退出國家隊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/421094?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/421094?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入面d傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fe824c709e52ef75382576e7da620c21ee25cc","tid":425780,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:46:23.000Z","msg":"碧基收撚左共產黨錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe3957f03f07ea6e059a815180be142527c1fa4","tid":425780,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"69bb6da6e292a829a125cccb2498afb7b397433f","tid":425780,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"係唔係都屈炒車先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4add3513eb3ac9d8cb57eccb3e90d32ee94876e9","tid":425780,"uid":25267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"肯定係佛朗哥返生用槍指住佢<br />\n死皇狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3335ac9f2aedc63445eb38e80782febed2152616","tid":425780,"uid":2974,"like":0,"disli